  "bench_knowledge": [
    "Surfactants above their CMC form micelles that stabilise foam. Any air-liquid interface created by dispensing rapidly or by blowout air bubbles generates persistent foam. Dispensing slowly along the tube wall prevents air entrainment. Touch-off tip on the wall instead of final blowout eliminates the last drop of air."
